<h1 class="h3">Terms of Service</h1>
<p class="meta-mono">Last updated: 2026-07-20</p>

<div class="text-body-secondary" style="max-width:70ch">
    <p>
        These terms cover use of <b>CalCrony</b> — the Discord bot, this web app, and its API — as
        operated by the maintainer of the
        <a href="https://github.com/JJWren/CalCrony" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CalCrony repository</a>
